Greeting Cards from Peepal Pol!

Hope you E2likedE2 the Freshie video.

As announced in the end of Freshie video, Bioscope Factory is going to hold
the first event next Wednesday (5th October, 2016) on

Video Editing S01E01: How to achieve a Film Look
Time: 6  8 PM
Venue: Loading...

The workshop series is a part of the many activities of Bioscope Factory.
As for the event, How to get a film look is about the basics of editing for
people:

    interested in editing

    who wish to know various processes of film making

    who want to find out what editing is

    why editing is an integral part of postproduction

People who want to come, please fill the form
 and download the software and
important exercise files from the link . We will
teach you things in video editing right from 0.

People who decide to come to the event at the last minute make sure the
last minute is before half an hour of the commencement of the event so that
you can load the software on your laptops at the venue. This is the first
module on editing, there are more to come. You can even come to find out if
you are interested in it.
People, laptops are mandatory. For those who do not have laptops, we will
have a few at the venue on first come first serve basis.

